646.1]}, {"text": "All of these free cash flows measures have limitations as they omit certain components of the overall cash flow statement", "bbox": [131.2, 675.2, 1148.9, 696.1]}, {"text": "and do not represent the residual cash flow available for discretionary expenditures. For example, these measures of free cash", "bbox": [84.4, 700.2, 1135.7, 721.1]}, {"text": "flows do not incorporate the portion of payments representing principal reductions of debt or cash payments for business", "bbox": [84.4, 725.2, 1096.2, 746.1]}, {"text": "acquisitions. Additionally, our mix of property and equipment acquisitions with cash or other financing options may change", "bbox": [84.4, 750.2, 1120.5, 771.1]}, {"text": "over time. Therefore, we believe it is important to view free cash flows measures only as a complement to our entire", "bbox": [84.4, 775.2, 1059.2, 796.1]}, {"text": "consolidated statements of cash flows.", "bbox": [84.4, 800.2, 409.4, 821.1]}, {"text": "Effect of Foreign Exchange Rates", "bbox": [112.5, 854.3, 398.2, 875.2]}, {"text": "Information regarding the effect of foreign exchange rates, versus the U.S. Dollar, on our net sales, operating expenses,", "bbox": [134.4, 889.7, 1133.3, 910.6]}, {"text": "and operating income is provided to show reported period operating results had the foreign exchange rates remained the same", "bbox": [84.4, 914.8, 1136.7, 935.7]}, {"text": "as those in effect in the comparable prior year periods. The effect on our net sales, operating expenses, and operating income is", "bbox": [84.4, 939.8, 1147.1, 960.7]}, {"text": "as follows (in millions):", "bbox": [84.4, 964.8, 289.4, 985.7]}, {"text": "Year Ended December 31, 2014", "bbox": [437.3, 1021.1, 637.3, 1035.7]}, {"text": "Year Ended December 31, 2015", "bbox": [684.1, 1021.1, 884.1, 1035.7]}, {"text": "Year Ended December 31, 2016", "bbox": [934.1, 1021.1, 1134.1, 1035.7]}, {"text": "As", "bbox": [445.0, 1060.7, 464.9, 1075.3]}, {"text": "Reported", "bbox": [424.0, 1075.3